The fast path is taken when TLB_FLAGS_MASK is all zero.

TLB_FORCE_SLOW is simply a TLB_FLAGS_MASK bit to force the slow path,
there are no other side effects.

Signed-off-by: Tony Nguyen <tony.nguyen@bt.com>
